# Mobile patterns

- Expo + TypeScript; call web API at `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL`
- Reuse types from `@tiki-acca/shared`
- Match web flows: auth, dashboard, group detail, submit leg
- Use `fetch` with `Authorization: Bearer <token>` from SecureStore
- Sign in via `POST /api/auth/mobile/sign-in`; sign up via `/api/auth/sign-up` then sign in
